      "body" : "I'd rather see any such possibility to enter sensitive information on the command line to be removed. It is not only `ps` output, but also history etc.",
      "created_at" : "2015-11-29T10:49:36Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/7122#issuecomment-160399013",
      "id" : 160399013,
      "issue_url" : "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/7122",
      "updated_at" : "2015-11-29T10:49:36Z",
      "url" : "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/comments/160399013",
